<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF616ADEFF8490FC1F0DBC08" pageId="154" pageNumber="915" type="activity">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF616ADEFF8490FC1F0DBC08" blockId="154.[120,1331,870,2089]" pageId="154" pageNumber="915">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF616ADEFF8490FC1F65BDF4" bold="true" box="[120,357,1701,1734]" pageId="154" pageNumber="915">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Call shape from one 
